  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Kidney Magnetic Resonance assessment before and after undergoing transcatheter aortic valve
      replacement
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Each patient will undergo Magnetic Resonance assessment of the kidneys before the TAVR. on
      the third to 7th day after the ATVR, a second MRI to the kidneys will be performed. we will
      assess the changes and new lesions between both MRI tests and will perform a qualitative and
      quantitative measurement.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
